high_descs: Walk over to the section of counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the metal table spoon off of the counter.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the stove.
Put the spoon in the pan that is on the front left burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the spoon in it off of the stove.
Walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the pan with the spoon in it into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a spoon in it in the sink.

high_descs: Take a step to the left to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Take a step to the right and face the stove.
Place the knife on the pan on the front left burner.
Pick up the pan with a knife in it on the stove.
Turn around and step forward to face the sink.
Place the pan with a spoon in it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a spoon on a pan plus move them to the sink.

high_descs: Turn left, walk just past the stove, turn right and face the cabinet just left of the stove.
Pick up the spoon lying on the counter left of the stove.
Turn right, walk slightly forward, then turn left to the stove.
Place the spoon on the plate that is on top of the stove.
Pick up the plate with the spoon on it.
Turn left, walk slightly forward, turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the plate with the spoon on it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the spoon and plate in the sink.
